<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html> 

  <head>     
  <meta property="og:title" content="Profile Activity"/>

  <title>Profile Activity</title> 
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <div style="min-width:550px;background-color:#3c3e44;color: #333333; text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 #fff; font-family: 'OpenSans', 'HelveticaNeue', 'Helvetica Neue', 'HelveticaNeueRoman', 'HelveticaNeue-Roman', 'Helvetica Neue Roman', 'TeXGyreHerosRegular', 'Helvetica', 'Tahoma', 'Geneva', 'Arial', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal;text-align:center;">
      <img src="https://www.supplybetter.com/assets/logo-7888d1412d5c568526ac6288f97c757a.png" alt="SupplyBetter Logo" style="margin:35px 0 35px;text-align:center">
      <div style="width: 540px; background-color: #f3f3f3; text-align: left; margin: 0 auto 40px; padding: 5px 5px 0; border-radius:3px;" bgcolor="#f3f3f3" align="left">
        <div style="padding:0 40px 15px; border-bottom:1px dashed #c0c0c8;">
          <div style="font-size:40px;font-weight: normal; margin-bottom:30px;">
          </div>
          <div style="width:460px; text-align: left; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; line-height:22px; margin:0 0 30px" align="left">
           		<p>
              We have customers asking about <%= @supplier.name %> on SupplyBetter!
              </p>
          </div>
          <div style="width:460px; text-align: left; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; line-height:22px;margin:0 0 30px" align="left">
            <p>
              On&nbsp;<a style="color: #333;" href=<%= "http://supplybetter.com#{@url_name_for_link}" %> target="_blank">your SupplyBetter profile</a>&nbsp;there have been:
              <ul>
                <% if @asks_hash["description_requested"] %>
                  <li><strong><%= pluralize(@asks_hash["description_requested"],"request")%></strong> for a company description</li>
                <% end %>
                <% if @asks_hash["machines_requested"] %>
                  <li><strong><%= pluralize(@asks_hash["machines_requested"],"request")%></strong> for what machines you use</li>
                <% end %>
                <% if @asks_hash["reviews_requested"] %>
                  <li><strong><%= pluralize(@asks_hash["reviews_requested"],"request")%></strong> for reviews from your past clients</li>
                <% end %>
              </ul>
              
              People who visit SupplyBetter looking for 3D Printing are interested in learning more about who you are and what you make. You can update your company details by making an account and&nbsp;<%= mail_to "claim-profile@supplybetter.com", "claiming your profile", subject: "Please create my supplier account so I can claim my profile", body: "I'd like to claim the profile for #{@supplier.name}. Please send me more information.", target: "_blank", style: "color: #333;" %>&nbsp;. Once your information is updated we'll be able to start connecting you to your potential customers.
              <br>
              <br>
              The best part? It's free to claim your profile. Free as in speech. 
            </p>
            <div style="text-shadow: none;">
              <tbody>
                <tr> 
                  <td style="width:580px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;padding:20px">
                    <%= mail_to "unsubscribe@supplybetter.com", "Claim Profile", subject: "Please create my supplier account so I can claim my profile", body: "I'd like to claim the profile for #{@supplier.name}. Please send me more information.", target: "_blank", style: "background-color:#00AED7;border:1px solid #0091B3!important;border-collapse:collapse;border-radius:3px;display:block;color:#fff;font-family:OpenSans, helvetica,arial,Verdana,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1;margin:0px auto;outline:none;padding:10px 20px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;width:150px;border-width:0;min-height:14px" %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </div>

            <p>
              Learn about the benefits of&nbsp;<a style="color: #333;" href="https://www.supplybetter.com/be_a_supplier" target="_blank">joining our supplier network.</a>&nbsp;<br>
              <br>
              As always, feel free to provide feedback or let us know if you have any questions by emailing&nbsp;<a style="color: #333; text-decoration:none">support@supplybetter.com.</a>&nbsp;<br>
              <br>
              Your friend in 3D Printing,<br>
              Matt Du Pont, CEO<br>
              SupplyBetter, Inc.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top:1px dashed #fff; padding:30px 10px; text-align:center; font-size:10px; font-weight:bold; color:#333; text-decoration:none">
          <p>You are receiving this email because your email address was linked to <%= @supplier.name %> on SupplyBetter.com.
          </p>
          <%= mail_to "unsubscribe@supplybetter.com", "Unsubscribe", subject: "Please unsubscribe me from future emails", body: "I no longer wish to receive SupplyBetter emails on behalf of #{@supplier.name}." %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:10px; font-weight:normal;color:#888;text-shadow:none;margin-bottom:45px;">
        &nbsp;<a style="text-decoration: none;color:#888" href="http://supplybetter.com" target="_blank">SupplyBetter, Inc.</a>&nbsp;&bull; 1688 Sacramento Street, #302, San Francisco, CA 94109
      </div>
      <br>
    </div>
  </body>    
</html>
